thread.title: Taft tennis hosts SSL championship

title: Taft tennis hosts SSL championship
text: Taft tennis hosts SSL championship The championship will take place Thursday and Friday Comment   Writer Posted Oct. 12, 2015 at 12:27 PM Posted Oct. 12, 2015 at 12:27 PM After defeating Robert F. Kennedy at home last Thursday, the Taft varsity girls tennis team closed out their regular season at home Tuesday. It will not be the last home match for Taft. This Thursday and Friday they will host the South Sequoiua League Championship with the matches starting Thursday at 2 p.m.   Writer
